Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Nun', 3: "One by one, according to order! Don't rush in!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nun', 3: "Even if you rushed in first, you won't be getting more food!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nun', 3: 'Five adults, a hundred and forty kids.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Soldier', 3: 'City 019 cannot take in as many refugees as it did before.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nun', 3: 'But we came a long way here!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nun', 3: 'But have you ever seen this many plump and well-fed kids queuing up?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nun', 3: 'This means they are tougher than the normal bunch and can take on more work in the city.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nun', 3: "Of course, your ol' sis here... I mean, I'm the one with exceptional caretaking abilities.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nun', 3: 'This amount of high-quality workforce is going to be a blessing to your...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nun', 3: 'Oh my, did you hear, children? Come now! Say thank you to Mr. Soldier!', 4: '1'}
